snippet.title: Amber Alexxa Taste Tests Diddy Ciroc Summer Colada and Gives Honest Review
snippet.description:
Dallas model/actress/host, Amber Alexxa, sits down with DJ Smallz and taste tests Diddy's newest flavor to his Ciroc Ultra-Premium Vodka line, a product for those of legal drinking age.

Have you had a chance to taste Diddy's Ciroc Summer Colada? Do You agree with Amber's review? Sound off by posting a comment below.
